     <h3> Aesthetics </h3> 
     <pre>
This website should be easy to read. And one user can find what they want. 
The links will help the user and take them to the page straight forward.
     </pre>
     
     <h4> Colour and Font styles </h4>
     <pre>
User will feel the colour of the page match. There will not be a strange colour. (like: green and red) 
All the pages are use the primary colour is around grey. The <span>Background colour</span> of the <span>ID header</span> is #595959 
and the word is white so have a sharp contrast. All the texts and pictures are in the middle. Centre make 
them in order and clear.  
    </pre>
     
